These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, february, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person who's birthday is in april##7
8. the chinese and the person who's birthday is in october have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person who's birthday is in june have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | february   | october     | april | june  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, snooker, scrabble
1. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person playing scrabble and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
4. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | domino | canasta | snooker      | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
House: cottage, tower, townhouse, modern
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the townhouse house is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
3. the tower house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the tower house is on the far left##1
5. the cottage house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
6. the townhouse house is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the tower house and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | tower    | townhouse   | cottage    | modern  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

