.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, puzzles, photography, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, reggae, trance
1. the fan hip-hop is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the fan indie is on the right of the fan reggae##1
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
4. the fan trance is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
5. the fan indie is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is sudoku and the fan trance have the same parity positions##9
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | sudoku | photography | video-games  | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | reggae             | indie          | trance | hip-hop    |

