.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, aquamarine, coral, lavender
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who likes coral is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the person who likes fuchsia have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the person who likes aquamarine have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
6. the person who likes aquamarine is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the person who likes lavender##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | fuchsia | coral | lavender  | aquamarine |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

