.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, entrepreneur, librarian, photographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, van, ship, car
1. the chef is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
2. the person driving the van and the librarian have the same parity positions##9
3. the chef is the person driving the car##1
4. the librarian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |  2   |     3     |      4       |
| Job   | entrepreneur | chef | librarian | photographer |
| Pet   | ship         | car | van    | snowmobile   |

