.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, entrepreneur, project-manager, pilot
4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, mouse, rabbit
1. the engineer is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the hamster##7
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the pilot is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
5. the entrepreneur is not the owner of the fish##6
6. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
7. the pilot and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | pilot | entrepreneur | engineer | project-manager |
| Pet     | hamster     | mouse     | rabbit     | fish    |

