.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, papaya, pepper, watermelon
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, goat, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
2. the person eating watermelon and the owner of the guinea-pig have the same parity positions##9
3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5
4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
6. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | pepper | broccoli   | papaya | watermelon |
| Transport   | goat   | rabbit | hamster    | guinea-pig      |

