.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, subway, helicopter
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, puzzles, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person driving the subway have different parity positions##9
5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |      3       |     4     |
| Food    | helicopter | train | bus   | subway   |
| Hobby   | skydiving  | puzzles   | magic-tricks | gardening |

