.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-12::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, d&b, indie, rock
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, iced-tea
1. the fan country is on the right of the fan indie##1
2. the fan indie is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
3. the fan rock and the person drinking almond-milk have the same parity positions##9
4. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan rock##1
5. the fan country is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |   3   |     4      |
