.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, nectarine, peach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, september, november, december
1. the person eating peach is not the person who's birthday is in december##6
2. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
3. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating garlic is the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the person eating peach and the person who's birthday is in june have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lemon   | peach    | nectarine | garlic    |
| Nationality   | december | june | november   | september |

