The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, disco, hip-hop, salsa
1. the coach and the fan salsa have the same parity positions##9
2. the fan salsa is not to the left of the coach##8
3. the engineer is somewhere between the fan d&b and the fan salsa##7
4. the fan salsa is somewhere between the fan hip-hop and the engineer##7
5. the fan disco is not the paramedic##6
6. the coach is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the scientist is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
