.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, chess, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, family, mystery
1. the person watching comedy movies is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
8. the person watching comedy movies and the person who's hobby is woodworking have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching family movies and the person who's hobby is chess have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | collecting   | board-games  | chess  | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | family | mystery | comedy      |

