.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-18::.
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, monopoly, canasta
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, hedgehog, rat
1. the person playing canasta and the owner of the cat have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person playing monopoly is not to the right of the owner of the cat##8
4. the person playing canasta is not to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##8
5. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hedgehog and the person playing scrabble have the same parity positions##9
7. the owner of the cat and the person playing monopoly have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | scrabble | canasta | mah-jongg | monopoly |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | fish   | rat        | cat            |

