.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, milk, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, march, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
2. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's birthday is in february have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | milk    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | march | february   | june   | may   |

